<emphasis id="12B04A613D74FF93FF4DFB38FEB0FA9D" bold="true" box="[199,347,1265,1291]" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">Description:</emphasis>
Male and female described by 
<bibRefCitation id="4455EB823D74FF93FD30FB38FC2FFA9A" author="Brescovit, A. D." box="[698,964,1265,1292]" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" pagination="1 - 187" refId="ref40616" refString="Brescovit, A. D. (1997) Revis &quot; o de Anyphaeninae Bertkau a nivel de generos na regi &quot; o neotropical (Araneae, Anyphaenidae). Revista Brasileira de Zoologia, 13, 1 - 187." type="journal article" year="1997">Brescovit, 1997: 35–36</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
